cancel last time…

164
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:17,470
When should we

165
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:18,640
reschedule?

166
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:20,140
I still owe you a meal.

167
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:22,440
Junjia,

168
00:11:22,810 --> 00:11:23,840
I...

169
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:29,580
It's okay.

170
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,610
I'll let you know
once I figure out a time.

171
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,460
See you tomorrow.

172
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:52,140
The fifth fret on a guitar

173
00:11:52,430 --> 00:11:54,810
is where chord transitions happen.

174
00:11:55,170 --> 00:11:57,370
Just like the distance between people—

175
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:59,180
sometimes

176
00:11:59,180 --> 00:12:01,910
you're close enough
to hear each other's breath,

177
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:04,030
but still far enough apart

178
00:12:04,090 --> 00:12:06,290
to never truly see each other's hearts.

179
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:09,760
Junior.

180
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:11,330
Senior Tie.

181
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:13,090
Senior Yuchen.

182
00:12:13,530 --> 00:12:14,590
Are you going home?

183
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:16,330
No, I'm going to work.

184
00:12:16,730 --> 00:12:17,900
Work?

185
00:12:18,970 --> 00:12:19,630
Is Senior He

186
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:20,900
not with you?

187
00:12:21,100 --> 00:12:21,840
He?

188
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,690
He's with Gu Yitong.

189
00:12:25,110 --> 00:12:26,710
Gu Yitong?

190
00:12:29,190 --> 00:12:30,780
I heard from the dance club

191
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:32,980
that Gu Yitong and He
are apparently dating.

192
00:12:32,980 --> 00:12:33,480
And

193
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:35,440
they seem to just get together.

194
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:37,240
I really envy him.

195
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,710
Stop thinking about it.

196
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:40,620
She's so pretty.

197
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:42,690
All right, go home and practice.

198
00:12:45,230 --> 00:12:48,850
[The moment before going on stage]

199
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,600
Gu Yitong and He are apparently dating.

200
00:13:11,530 --> 00:13:12,730
[Are you okay?][Or are you still at work?]

201
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:14,050
[Are you at the convenience store?]

202
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,620
[Why aren't you replying?]

203
00:13:35,170 --> 00:13:36,000
You're here.

204
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:38,410
Where is Jiayi?

205
00:13:39,030 --> 00:13:41,210
Isn't he usually the first one
to show up for practice?

206
00:13:41,210 --> 00:13:42,010
He

207
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:43,290
took the day off today,

208
00:13:43,570 --> 00:13:45,100
but he still came to school.

209
00:13:45,690 --> 00:13:47,620
So he just took leave from the club.

210
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,300
You…

211
00:13:53,330 --> 00:13:55,960
Weren't you two
getting pretty close lately?

212
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:57,790
What's going on now?

213
00:14:07,710 --> 00:14:08,370
Jia...

214
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:27,460
In these days that feel like fog,

215
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:29,100
like a dream

216
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,330
like a misunderstanding,

217
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:34,100
I've always wanted to ask—

218
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:46,280
what

219
00:14:46,980 --> 00:14:48,550
exactly are we

220
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,550
to each other?

221
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:03,810
[Fifth fret—the moment relationships
start to shift out of tune]

222
00:15:57,100 --> 00:15:57,880
Diaoqin,

223
00:15:59,130 --> 00:16:01,410
are you going to practice
at the outdoor court?

224
00:16:01,410 --> 00:16:02,150
Yes.

225
00:16:02,180 --> 00:16:03,510
I want to watch you play.

226
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:04,160
Sure.

227
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:05,060
Let's go.

228
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:08,360
There's a basketball court
in the park nearby.

229
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:17,640
Good thing you reminded me
in English class last time.

230
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:20,570
Otherwise I would've gotten scolded
by the teacher.

231
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:22,960
Really?

232
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:23,810
Besides...

233
00:16:23,810 --> 00:16:24,530
Jiayi,

234
00:16:25,070 --> 00:16:27,130
why didn't you come to the club today?

235
00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:34,540
I was tutoring Diaoqin.

236
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:39,540
Is that so?

237
00:17:00,390 --> 00:17:01,230
Junjia.

238
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:03,210
Let's go.

239
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:04,290
Class is starting.

240
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:17,940
[Are you okay?]

241
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,349
[Or are you still at work?]

242
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:20,880
[Are you at the convenience store?]

243
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:22,310
[Why aren't you replying?]

244
00:17:21,660 --> 00:17:23,040
You're not a kid anymore.

245
00:17:23,040 --> 00:17:26,500
I still have to remind you about
your follow-up appointments.

246
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:30,030
Your dad's work in Shanghai
is almost done,

247
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:32,140
and he'll be home more often soon.

248
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:41,060
I know you're closer to your dad,

249
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:44,280
but I just want you
to take care of yourself.

250
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:46,310
At least go to your check-ups on time.

251
00:17:46,310 --> 00:17:47,910
Keep your condition stable.

252
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:49,700
You know how serious it can get

253
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:51,160
if it relapses, don't you?

254
00:18:00,770 --> 00:18:02,070
I knew you'd be here.

255
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:05,470
What's been up with you these days?

256
00:18:05,470 --> 00:18:07,330
Did you quarrel with your junior?

257
00:18:19,260 --> 00:18:20,660
Let me ask you something.

258
00:18:21,290 --> 00:18:21,860
Go ahead.

259
00:18:23,130 --> 00:18:24,160
I have a friend.

260
00:18:24,990 --> 00:18:25,320
He...

261
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:25,820
Wait.

262
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:28,270
You have other friends?

263
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,230
Tell me.

264
00:18:33,260 --> 00:18:35,800
What's wrong with your friend?

265
00:18:36,670 --> 00:18:37,890
He knows someone,

266
00:18:38,850 --> 00:18:39,750
and

267
00:18:39,770 --> 00:18:41,700
he really cares about that person.

268
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:43,010
But

269
00:18:43,040 --> 00:18:44,970
suddenly that person ignored him.

270
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:46,490
Do you know why?

271
00:18:52,050 --> 00:18:53,650
I'm really talking to a wall.

272
00:18:53,830 --> 00:18:54,630
Forget what I said.

273
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:56,450
But I was born in the Year of the Dog.

274
00:18:56,450 --> 00:18:57,080
Woof!

275
00:18:57,130 --> 00:18:57,520
I'm leaving.

276
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:58,230
Wait.

277
00:18:58,270 --> 00:18:59,670
I'm just kidding.

278
00:18:59,670 --> 00:19:01,530
You really have no sense of humor?

279
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:07,940
There are several possibilities.

280
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:09,830
First,

281
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:11,480
that person might be a player.

282
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,010
No way.

283
00:19:12,010 --> 00:19:12,530
A jerk.

284
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:13,690
That's impossible.

285
00:19:15,740 --> 00:19:16,440
Besides,

286
00:19:17,420 --> 00:19:18,750
I never said it was a guy.

287
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:23,280
There's another possibility.

288
00:19:24,470 --> 00:19:26,270
Either he changed his feelings,

289
00:19:26,590 --> 00:19:28,360
or your friend

290
00:19:28,390 --> 00:19:29,710
might have done something

291
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:32,640
that made that person
not want to talk to him anymore.

292
00:19:37,170 --> 00:19:37,700
Nice.

293
00:19:37,730 --> 00:19:38,130
Here.

294
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:44,040
Can you cover for me?

295
00:20:05,420 --> 00:20:06,120
So cold.

296
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:06,880
Is it cold?

297
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:09,460
The temperature

298
00:20:10,420 --> 00:20:11,990
can freeze your bad mood.

299
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:16,050
I'm not in a bad mood.

300
00:20:16,300 --> 00:20:17,700
I'm in a good mood.

301
00:20:17,730 --> 00:20:18,830
I'm happy

302
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:20,020
every single day.

303
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,660
No one can

304
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,280
be happy every single day.

305
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,090
I am.

306
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:27,090
Let me tell you,

307
00:20:27,110 --> 00:20:28,240
I was even the "happiness champion"

308
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:30,060
in kindergarten.

309
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:37,730
That sounds more like

310
00:20:37,730 --> 00:20:39,370
"class troublemaker."

311
00:20:41,470 --> 00:20:42,620
How do you know

312
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:44,700
that I was naughty when I was a kid?

313
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:53,860
Actually, I know

314
00:20:57,080 --> 00:20:58,930
you are avoiding He.

315
00:21:01,810 --> 00:21:02,680
I don't know

316
00:21:02,710 --> 00:21:04,650
why you're avoiding him,

317
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:07,290
but from what I can see,

318
00:21:08,530 --> 00:21:10,450
you don't actually want to do this,

319
00:21:10,450 --> 00:21:11,080
right?

320
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:17,100
Is it because of

321
00:21:17,910 --> 00:21:20,310
the relationship between He and Gu Yitong?

322
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:26,240
I'm really not thinking about that.

323
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:31,070
We only see things

324
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:32,900
from one angle,

325
00:21:33,390 --> 00:21:34,850
and even with our two ears.

326
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:37,250
If you have any questions,

327
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,380
just ask the other person.

328
00:21:42,010 --> 00:21:43,510
At least make sure

329
00:21:44,490 --> 00:21:45,880
that you're happy.

330
00:21:53,870 --> 00:21:54,540
Jiayi,

331
00:21:56,290 --> 00:21:57,550
what's wrong with you?

332
00:22:05,330 --> 00:22:06,930
I bought you a new wrist wrap.

333
00:22:09,110 --> 00:22:10,340
Change it if you want.

334
00:22:22,770 --> 00:22:23,780
[Are you okay?][Or are you still at work?]

335
00:22:23,810 --> 00:22:24,920
[Are you at the convenience store?]

336
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:25,980
[Why aren't you replying?]

337
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:32,460
Either he changed his feelings,

338
00:22:32,900 --> 00:22:34,810
or your friend

339
00:22:34,830 --> 00:22:36,040
might have done something

340
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:38,970
that made that person
not want to talk to him anymore.

341
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:45,260
[I want to know if I did something wrong.]

342
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:52,580
But no matter what happens,

343
00:22:52,610 --> 00:22:54,480
I hope your friend

344
00:22:54,500 --> 00:22:56,600
can speak his mind.

345
00:25:29,930 --> 00:25:33,240
[Preview of the Next Episode]

346
00:25:30,710 --> 00:25:31,450
Jiayi.

347
00:25:32,990 --> 00:25:33,700
Jiayi!

348
00:25:38,600 --> 00:25:39,800
Am I really

349
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:41,800
in a place to love someone right now?

350
00:25:44,940 --> 00:25:47,270
Are you free this weekend?

351
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:50,320
I want to talk to you about something—

352
00:25:50,320 --> 00:25:52,030
about the two of us.
